text: Isomerida albicollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Laporte in 1840. It is known from Brazil, French Guiana and Colombia.BioLib.cz - Isomerida albicollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1840
title: Isomerida albicollis
